{"tid":1518020,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"加碼外國勢力！唔好忘記可以爭撫養權嘅英國！","createTime":"2019-08-30T06:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T06:06:12.000Z","uid":314604,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e823e28ddb7588ee17a56a6c3e02052e72244d0","tid":1518020,"uid":314604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:06:00.000Z","msg":"宜家各國都表態支持香港，先唔好理佢哋會唔會插手干預，總之愈多外國焦點，香港就愈係國際議題。全部人都知香港係中共春袋，中共成日大支野話要做一哥，你估大家樂唔樂於見到中共仆街？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1508875/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1508875/page/2</a><br />\n引用前英領ching嘅詳盡post，英國已經開到聲考慮為BNO平權，我地要落力啲比人知我地要幫助，同埋我地要英國爭撫養權，做出國際表態已經會令中共多一重制肘！<br />\n<br />\nching有提到：<br />\n有咩我地可以做呢？<br />\n1.開聲請求英國協助 - 中共擺到明唔理 係咪要請求英國介入呢<br />\n2.比人知道BNO既存在 - 即使係英國MPs, 大部分都唔知道BNO係咩 我地要更加比英國甚至外國知道，香港係有200幾300萬既英國國民，所以英國更加有責任去幫香港保護國民。BNO都係一個非常之不公平違反人權既存在，所以我地要更加講呢件事擺上國際。<br />\n<br />\n宜家已經有兩件事大家可以做，要把握機會喺十月一號前搞大佢，<span style=\"color: red;\">慶佢國慶老母呀</span>！<br />\n<br />\n1. BNO平權petition，9月20號deadline，仲爭2萬8千個簽名！<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=8d4f3acf\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 9月1去英國領事館請願，1400去完先去機場都仲OK！一定要比記者特別係外媒影到相！ 好多人都唔知，幫手推出去呀！特別係有BNO嘅人！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qjAogJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqjAogJQ.jpg&h=9f93a63a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命 </span>"},{"pid":"9d8232c21d9476af8a6b2b5ad975b2df630df5cf","tid":1518020,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=c481fe86\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=ad81ab2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=5a8146ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"}]}